GRAPH <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Digest_SolutionArchetypes> {
  <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Digest_SolutionArchetypes> a narr:Digest ;
    narr:digestOf <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#SolutionArchetypes> ;
    narr:childCount "38"^^xsd:integer ;
    narr:generatedFrom "8d8c27340c2636713f8a3aa793053637113596bc" ;
    narr:narration """This hub gathers solution archetypes, demo scripts, use-case taxonomies, and engagement playbooks. The backbone taxonomy has evolved: an earlier three-way use-case frame (May 2026) distinguished [governing a human team](narr:Narrative_UseCase1GoverningHumanTeam) (ARB, leadership), [agentic steering at one-model and ecosystem scale](narr:Narrative_UseCase2AgenticSteering) (flagged as underrepresented), and [steering the shared process across engagements](narr:Narrative_UseCase3SharedProcessSteering). A Jul 2 reframe sharpened this into [Discovery / Onboarding / Governance](narr:Narrative_ThreeUseCaseTaxonomy), explicitly demoting 'organizational memory' to a governance sub-use-case and naming [Onboarding](narr:Narrative_OnboardingUseCase) as a distinct lifecycle phase between the other two. A [collaboration-shape taxonomy](narr:Narrative_CollaborationTaxonomy) (Individual→Self/Team/Many, Team→Many) remains flagged as missing from the strategy doc. Concrete demos cluster around the enterprise customer: [QA onboarding](narr:SolutionArchetype_QAOnboarding) ('killer sales demo'), [CEO knowledge transfer](narr:SolutionArchetype_CEOKnowledgeTransfer), and [code quality through business context](narr:SolutionArchetype_CodeQualityThroughContext). Onboarding methodology moved from a [three-part seeding pattern](narr:Narrative_ThreePartSeedingPattern) (topic analysis over direct ingestion) toward a [hub-collection method at volume](narr:Narrative_HubCollectionMethodAtVolume) (one memory per topic cluster, not per transcript), with [bulk ingestion via AI summarization](narr:Narrative_BulkIngestionValidMethod) rehabilitated as valid (May 21 correction). Consulting archetypes span [module-as-deliverable](narr:Narrative_ConsultingModuleDeliverable) (deck as derived artifact), a [three-phase engagement arc](narr:Narrative_EngagementArcThreePhase) (gift → backfill diagnostic → ongoing stream), and a [productized narrative-strategy report](narr:Narrative_NarrativeStrategyReport) (2-4 week NDA'd fixed deliverable). Sales motion is anchored by [sponsor≠champion](narr:Narrative_SponsorVsChampionPlaybook) and [POC/MSA in parallel](narr:Narrative_POCMSAParallelism) (Tony, Apr 2026). A [five-question discovery framework](narr:Narrative_FiveQuestionDiscoveryFramework) doubles as call-one structure with a disqualification rule. Healthcare adds the [proposal artifact](narr:Narrative_ProposalArtifactPractitioner) lock-in; [extraction scope](narr:Narrative_ExtractionScopeOrgWorldview) reframes 'domain' as organizational worldview.""" ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Archetype_YCDemoFlow> ;
