    narr:keyPhrase [ narr:text "bulk ingestion via AI summarization is a deliberate, successful method she advised the customer's chief architect to use for the enterprise customer's ARB transcripts" ; narr:phraseSource <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_BulkIngestionValidMethod> ] ;
    narr:keyPhrase [ narr:text "The deck is a derived artifact; the real value is the perspective shift." ; narr:phraseSource <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Obs_DeckIsArtifact> ] ;
    narr:keyPhrase [ narr:text "aswritten would keep what Bob thinks and what Anna thinks and what Charlie thinks in the provenance. They're different perspectives. I think there is value in marketing this as a discovery tool." ; narr:phraseSource <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Obs_DiscoveryConsultantBobAnnaCharlieQuote> ] ;
    narr:keyPhrase [ narr:text "Disqualification rule: no answers to questions two and three means friendly or pass, not buyer." ; narr:phraseSource <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_FiveQuestionDiscoveryFramework> ] ;
    narr:keyPhrase [ narr:text "you'd not just get the transcript, and you wouldn't be getting \"oh, Claude thinks you should do this\" — which would be terrible, because why does Claude think that?" ; narr:phraseSource <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Obs_DiscoveryConsultantDiscoveryToolQuote> ] ;
    narr:keyPhrase [ narr:text "it's steering the entire ecosystem and process around technical development, which is functionally the same thing as ARB" ; narr:phraseSource <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Obs_UseCase2AgenticScalesQuote> ] ;
    narr:keyPhrase [ narr:text "Process governance and process steering for aligning the commonalities and shared process between different engagements, different clients, different processes" ; narr:phraseSource <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Obs_UseCase3Quote> ] ;
    narr:keyPhrase [ narr:text "The meta contract is really a proposal, like we might pitch a enterprise company" ; narr:phraseSource <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Obs_ScarletProposalQuote> ] ;
    narr:variation [ narr:text "Onboarding methodology is contested: the three-part seeding pattern (May 1) explicitly rejected direct historical ingestion as a trap, but the May 21 correction rehabilitated bulk AI summarization as valid — the two sit in tension over what 'safe' ingestion means." ; narr:over <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_ThreePartSeedingPattern> ; narr:over <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_BulkIngestionValidMethod> ] ;
    narr:variation [ narr:text "The Jul 2 three-use-case reframe (Discovery/Onboarding/Governance) supersedes the May 26 three-use-case frame (Governing/Agentic/Shared-Process) — the earlier frame is still in the graph and an agent reaching for 'the use-case taxonomy' may find either." ; narr:over <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_ThreeUseCaseTaxonomy> ; narr:over <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_UseCase1GoverningHumanTeam> ; narr:over <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_UseCase2AgenticSteering> ; narr:over <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_UseCase3SharedProcessSteering> ] ;
    narr:variation [ narr:text "The collaboration-shape taxonomy (Individual→Self/Team/Many, Team→Many) is flagged as structurally missing from the strategy doc's archetype model — a gap, not a resolved position." ; narr:over <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_CollaborationTaxonomy> ; narr:over <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Obs_CollaborationTaxonomyList> ] ;
    narr:variation [ narr:text "The self-serve demo design argues for running on aswritten's own perspective with honesty beats as the lead — a different demo philosophy than the enterprise-customer-scenario demos (QA onboarding, CEO transfer) that dominate the archetype cluster." ; narr:over <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_SelfServeDemoOnOwnPerspective> ; narr:over <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#SolutionArchetype_QAOnboarding> ; narr:over <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#SolutionArchetype_CEOKnowledgeTransfer> ] ;
    narr:variation [ narr:text "Consulting delivery has three competing shapes that are not fully reconciled: module-as-deliverable (perspective over deck), the three-phase arc (gift→backfill→stream), and the productized narrative-strategy report (fixed 2-4 week NDA'd engagement) — each implies a different pricing and scoping logic." ; narr:over <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_ConsultingModuleDeliverable> ; narr:over <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_EngagementArcThreePhase> ; narr:over <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_NarrativeStrategyReport> ] ;
    narr:variation [ narr:text "Refract and Registry were removed as product features (Mar 2026) — any archetype that previously relied on them as delivery mechanisms is implicitly affected, though no child explicitly reconciles this with the current archetype set." ; narr:over <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Position_RemoveRefractProduct> ] ;
    narr:writer "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.6" .
}